message.body: /me sings "I don't dream about anyone, except my self..."
@basxto@zid: Lol not anymore. It was a Smiths lyric.
All this talk of dreams and what not
@iforgotmyusernam@zv: Happened to me a lot as a kid too, seemed to trail off as I got older
Used to freak me out because you are awake but cannot move, you have to sort of force yourself to wake up
I tend to only have dreams I remember during times of stress, when everything is going easy I sleep like a log straight through.
we spend so much of our lives in a sleep state, I have always thought the brain is doing more than just idling waiting to boot back up?
maybe our dreams lives are just as important as our waking lives? meh, its beyond me anyway
